=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gtk4::GestureZoom
=head1 Description

B<Gnome::Gtk4::GestureZoom> is a L<Gnome::Gtk4::Gesture|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/Gesture> for 2-finger pinch/zoom gestures.

Whenever the distance between both tracked sequences changes, the
I<scale-changed> signal is emitted to report
the scale factor.

