=begin pod
=head1 Signals

=comment -----------------------------------------------------------------------
=head3 scale-changed

Emitted whenever the distance between both tracked sequences changes.

=begin code
method handler (
  gdouble $scale,
  Int :$_handle_id,
  N-GObject :$_native-object,
  Gnome::Gtk4::GestureZoom :$_widget,
  *%user-options
)
=end code

=item $scale; Scale delta, taking the initial state as 1:1.
=item $_handle_id; The registered event handler id.
=item $_native-object; The native object provided by the Raku object which registered this event. This is a native B<Gnome::Gtk4::GestureZoom> object.
=item %user-options; A list of named arguments provided by L<.register-signal() in class Object|/content-docs/api2/reference/GObject/Object#register-signal>.

